(commands when installed)
on   #activates 
off  #disables 
(sudo required)



HOW TO INSTALL 

step 1: the security-startup.sh & on & off file(s) should be moved to /usr/local/bin/

step 2: run: chmod +x /usr/local/bin/on & chmod +x /usr/local/bin/security-startup.sh & chmod +x /usr/local/bin/off

# takes about 2 minutes of your time, but saves alot. 
